```
Solution.sln
src/
├── MyApp.Domain/
├── MyApp.Application/
├── MyApp.Infrastructure/
└── MyApp.Api/
tests/
├── MyApp.Domain.Tests/
├── MyApp.Application.Tests/
├── MyApp.Infrastructure.Tests/
